Betty Amann https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Betty_Amann 0 Philippine "Betty" Amann (March 10, 1907 – August 3, 1990) was a German-American film actress of Jewish descent. She began her film career in the United States with the film The Kick-Off (1926).
